text: Rhum can mean a number of things: *Rùm, a Scottish island also known as "Rhum" from Victorian times until 1991 *Rhum agricole or cane juice rum, a style of rum distilled from sugar cane juice rather than molasses * island class ferry *Rhum gasfield, a gas field in the UK sector of the North Sea *Rhum (actor) a French actor and clown, friend of Jacques Tati and star of the short film Gai dimanche ==See also== * Rhumb (disambiguation)
title: Rhum
